Login
import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute, Router } from '@angular/router'; import { AppServiceService } from 'src/app/service/app-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-navbar', templateUrl: './navbar.component.html', styleUrls: ['./navbar.component.scss'], }) export class NavbarComponent { selectedCategory = ''; loader: boolean = false; categoryList: any[] = []; username: string = ''; constructor( public apiService: AppServiceService, private route: ActivatedRoute, private router: Router ) { this.username = this.apiService.logedInUser.username; if (this.username == '' || this.username == undefined) { this.router.navigate(['/login'], { state: { pageTitle: 'login' }, }); return; } } }
